item.title: Subscription Success
item.description: What’s Next? As you can see, we already started the setup process and within a few minutes, you will receive: A welcome email with the URL and credentials to your new container registry Order confirmation email from our subscription management system While you ar waiting In the meantime, you can check out the following resources: Blog Frequently Asked Questions Improve your containerized workflow Help Support Chat is the best way to contact us for real-time support and technical problems.
